&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;336&quot; data-end=&quot;353&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;339&quot; data-end=&quot;353&quot;&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;355&quot; data-end=&quot;739&quot;&gt;Heritage is a modern global investment office built by a collective of respected families and entrepreneurs with over a century of business-building experience. We provide privileged access to top-performing alternative assets, superior portfolio construction, and a technology-enabled open-architecture platform connecting clients to some of the world’s most exclusive opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
