&lt;p data-start=&quot;973&quot; data-end=&quot;1132&quot;&gt;We believe in alignment. We invest alongside our clients with real skin in the game, applying the same standards and governance used for the founding families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1134&quot; data-end=&quot;1348&quot;&gt;We believe in technology. Our advanced digital platform centralizes, analyses, and benchmarks portfolios across managers, strategies, and asset classes, enabling better decision-making and risk management at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
